        'guide.theme.desc': 'You can choose from 4 themes in the settings panel: Classic, Bento, Terminal, or Minimal. Each theme has its own configuration options. Switching themes will not lose settings from other themes.',
        'guide.classic.title': 'Classic Theme',
        'guide.classic.desc': 'Standard icon grid layout with a frosted glass card background on hover. Configurable options include: container width (400-1400px), columns (3-8), border radius, card opacity, frosted glass blur, and icon size. The number of columns automatically shrinks based on the number of sites to avoid empty columns.',
        'guide.bento.title': 'Bento Theme',
        'guide.bento.desc': 'Two layout modes are available:<br />1. <strong>Dynamic layout</strong> (default): Card size is determined by click count using a Treemap algorithm. Sites with more clicks occupy larger areas, and new sites also have an initial area. Click counts are snapshotted on page load, so clicking does not cause immediate re-layout.<br />2. <strong>Fixed grid</strong>: All cards are equally sized and arranged in the configured number of columns.<br />Configurable options include: container width, gap (4-32px), border radius, card opacity, frosted glass blur, icon size, layout mode toggle, and fixed-mode column count.',
